                            <comment id="40775" author="pjones" created="Mon, 18 Jun 2012 14:55:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jay&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will take this up with you offline&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="40772" author="jaylan" created="Mon, 18 Jun 2012 14:11:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is no activity on this LU for almost 6 months. This fix is very important to use. Could you upgrade the priority? Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="25286" author="hongchao.zhang" created="Fri, 30 Dec 2011 02:57:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the patch is tracked at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,1908&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,1908&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
