the patch is under creating and test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24751" author="jaylan" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2011 15:04:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I cherry-picked Oracle&apos;s patch for our nas-1.8.6 branch without a problem. But, the patch applied to code that do not exist in 2.1. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our Lustre system admin consider this a very useful feature to them and we need your expertise to port the feature to 2.1. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
